These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, cycling, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | water-polo | cycling | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, nectarine, pineapple
1. the person eating nectarine is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating raspberry is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | raspberry | pineapple | nectarine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | card-games | collecting | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, indie, classical
1. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | folk | classical | indie |

 #################################

 
